{"tid":149970,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蘭貴芳邪骨　打飛機要700蚊","createTime":"2017-03-09T16:06:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-10T06:12:53.000Z","uid":26769,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7d6aa969df248695ce1da8571e0a73db2a4ad9c4","tid":149970,"uid":26769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T16:06:55.000Z","msg":"【蘭桂芳邪骨】按摩院提供手淫服務$700　警拘8女子<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/article/76900/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Farticle%2F76900%2F&d=iLyAB%2BOE6twWPMF9W2uC6gCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=c6405f0f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/article/76900/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/461361/xlarge/d80219197cf8764b5e58b795f5c6eec1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F461361%2Fxlarge%2Fd80219197cf8764b5e58b795f5c6eec1.jpg&h=5e3e319b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中區警區特別職務隊人員今日進行「雷霆一七」行動打擊罪行，於中環蘭桂芳掃蕩色情事業，並出動3名警員放蛇，行動中搗破一間俗稱「邪骨」的不良按摩院，拘捕一名按摩院女主持人及7名女子，包括5名內也女子，涉嫌經營賣淫場所及違反逗留條件等。警方在行動中檢獲一批按摩用具，包括按摩油、按摩床及毛巾等。<br />\n<br />\n另類按摩手淫服務<br />\n<br />\n中區警區特別職務隊督察黃子盛指，上址營運約一年，共有6間房，主要於網上招徠客人提供按摩服務，如是熟客或有人介紹，則會提供手淫服務，每次收費約700元。黃指該場所大多招待熟客及外籍人士，暫未發現為黑社會操控。<br />\n<br />\n黃子盛指行動出動12名警員，其中3人為放蛇人員，共拘捕8人，其年齡介乎29至42歲，其中包括一名35歲姓韓女主持人，涉嫌經營賣淫場所，另外2名本地女子及5名持雙程證女子，分別涉嫌協助經營賣淫場所及違反逗留條件。各人仍被扣留調查。"},{"pid":"00cf9b791cbe1e8b2ef2bb29582aefd0b082d4fb","tid":149970,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T16:08:07.000Z","msg":"標題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲以為係新場"},{"pid":"98fe1c430c9d2a01abf34f16e4adebbd0cae3661","tid":149970,"uid":26769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T16:09:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>標題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲以為係新場</blockquote><br />\nCHING去開邊個場呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7704fa2286f429c5b0da31dface144501b1b19a3","tid":149970,"uid":36238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T16:10:32.000Z","msg":"29-42<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e6ff28c4a849d5a6d1872e4c704e2bb71a3e1ba","tid":149970,"uid":26769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T16:30:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>29-42<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實是咪陀地年紀都比較大<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b7fb43ad08aa8362d3f491d565128a9dce24aed","tid":149970,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T16:34:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>29-42<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實是咪陀地年紀都比較大<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n拘捕一名按摩院女主持人及7名女子，包括5名內女子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5420b752146d6e1514361b9afb7cf88244b58b72","tid":149970,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T16:34:24.000Z","msg":"並出動3名警員放蛇<br />\n<br />\n幾好命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點做到呢d位"},{"pid":"2c2eb70761836a5660408f807b2537d3dc86e79a","tid":149970,"uid":44210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T17:06:26.000Z","msg":"係因為大陸落黎先拉定係本身都犯法?<br />\n香港咁多骨場唔拉晒既?"},{"pid":"64f1a6d460516153778e99391685198cc3f46932","tid":149970,"uid":68746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T17:11:35.000Z","msg":"大陸骨場過咗25都唔請<br />\n走落香港又可以搵港豬笨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4533f182d748cd5d8b86aff6821cb9e0699d25a4","tid":149970,"uid":51857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T17:30:58.000Z","msg":"過左30都出老態啦呀姐 4章幾點起機呀<br />\n仲收700<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fd1d43bc77978db42080b27f76d9bf03b206c26","tid":149970,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T06:12:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>並出動3名警員放蛇<br />\n<br />\n幾好命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點做到呢d位</blockquote><br />\n呢單冇咁著數啦<br />\n打飛機冇得屌"}]}